sentences: Haley Hannah Heynderickx (born May 28, 1993) is an American singer-songwriter from Portland, Oregon.
In 2016, she released her debut EP, Fish Eyes.
Her first full-length album, I Need to Start a Garden, was released in March 2018 on Mama Bird Recording Co.
Heynderickx was born in Stockton, California to a Filipino-American family and grew up in Forest Grove, Oregon, where she learned to sing in church.
